# 📊 PayRecover MENA — Full Project Analysis & Improvement Plan

## ❓ What is PayRecover?

**PayRecover** is a **SaaS tool for MENA SMEs** (clinics, gyms, coaches) that automates payment recovery through **WhatsApp & SMS reminders**. The idea is to help small businesses stop chasing payments manually by automating invoice follow-ups.

> **Target Market:** Egypt, UAE, KSA, Jordan, Bahrain — clinics, gyms, personal coaches
> **Pricing Model:** Basic ($29/mo) and Pro ($59/mo)

---

## 🏗️ Current Architecture

| Layer | Status |
|---|---|
| **Framework** | Next.js 15 (App Router) + TypeScript |
| **Styling** | TailwindCSS 4 |
| **Charts** | Recharts |
| **AI** | Gemini API key configured (but **not used anywhere**) |
| **Animations** | `motion` library installed (but **barely used**) |
| **Backend / API** | ❌ None — no API routes exist |
| **Database** | ❌ None — all data is hardcoded mock data |
| **Authentication** | ❌ None — "Sign In" just links to `/dashboard` |
| **Real Integrations** | ❌ None — WhatsApp, SMS, payment gateways are all UI-only |

### File Structure (8 source files total)

```
app/
├── page.tsx                    ← Landing page (hero, features, pricing)
├── layout.tsx                  ← Root layout (Inter font, metadata)
├── globals.css                 ← Just "@import tailwindcss"
└── dashboard/
    ├── layout.tsx              ← Dashboard shell (sidebar + header)
    ├── page.tsx                ← Overview (metrics cards + chart + invoice table)
    ├── invoices/page.tsx       ← Clients & Invoices (table + create modal)
    ├── reminders/page.tsx      ← Automations (WhatsApp/SMS templates)
    └── settings/page.tsx       ← Settings (profile, gateways, notifications)
lib/utils.ts                    ← cn() utility only
hooks/use-mobile.ts             ← Mobile breakpoint hook
```

---

## 🔴 Critical Issues (Must Fix)

### 1. No Backend / No Database
- **Every single data point** is hardcoded in the component files
- Creating an invoice only adds to local React state — refreshing the page resets everything
- No persistence at all

### 2. No Authentication
- "Sign In" button simply navigates to `/dashboard`
- No user accounts, no sessions, no protected routes
- Anyone can access the dashboard

### 3. No Real Integrations
- **WhatsApp buttons** → do nothing
- **SMS buttons** → do nothing
- **Payment gateway connections** (Paymob, Tap, Stripe) → do nothing
- **Search** → not functional
- **Download PDF** → not functional
- **Notification bell** → not functional

### 4. Sidebar Navigation Not Active-State Aware
- The sidebar always highlights "Overview" regardless of the current page (hardcoded `bg-emerald-50`)
- No `usePathname()` to detect the active route

### 5. No Mobile Sidebar
- Sidebar is `hidden md:flex` — on mobile, there's no way to navigate between dashboard pages
- [use-mobile.ts](file:///home/mina/Desktop/PayRecover/hooks/use-mobile.ts) hook exists but is unused

